SL-CP version 0.05
==================

The Silver Lining Networks Captive Portal

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

mod_perl2

